## Synopsis
Practical 2 of Fundamentals of Programming COMP1005/5005

## Contents
README – readme file for Practical 2
bucket1.py - use a python list for items in a bucket list
bucket2.py - bucket list builder
assorted.py - selecting random biscuits from a pack
strings1.py - Read in a string and print it in reverse using a loop and a method call
strings2.py: Extended Version of Strings1
fish.py - ASCII Art work of swimming fish
activity7.py - ASCII art work of a moving eyes
darts.py - Calculating PIE with darts
cointoss.py - simulate tossing a coin multiple times
VendingMachine.py - Simulate Vending Machine Transactions.

## Dependencies
tabulate - tabulate package is used for format console outputs

